Package: nanopoRe
Type: Package
Title: Accessory Methods for the Analysis of Oxford Nanopore Technologies DNA Sequence Data
Version: 0.2.5
Author: Stephen Rudd <stephen.rudd@nanoporetech.com>
Maintainer: Stephen Rudd <stephen.rudd@nanoporetech.com>
Description: A collection of utilities used by the Oxford Nanopore Technologies DNA sequence 
    analysis tutorials. These tutorials provide a collection of best-practise workflows that 
    demonstrate examples of how Nanopore sequence data may be used in applied bioinformatics 
    workflows.
